'''Gluss'sa'Nikto''', or '''Pale Nikto''', were a [[Nikto/Legends|Nikto]] [[Subspecies/Legends|subspecies]].<ref name="The Essential Guide to Alien Species" /> They came from the [[Gluss'elta Islands]] of [[Kintan/Legends|Kintan]], causing them to be natural sailors. They had white-gray skin, eye-horns like the [[Kadas'sa'Nikto/Legends|Kadas'sa'Nikto]], and fins similar to those of the [[Esral'sa'Nikto/Legends|Esral'sa'Nikto]], but smaller. [[Xenobiologist/Legends|Xenobiologists]] believed the first Gluss'sa'Nikto to have been born of a Kadas'sa'Nikto who mated with an Esral'sa'Nikto.

